{"tid":1901663,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始：無證據顯示醫管局對罷工醫護「秋後算帳」","createTime":"2020-02-28T02:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T05:16:27.000Z","uid":212626,"like":9,"dislike":215,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"5c2caeefab2024fc77a97cd13c526b4c3f425724","tid":1901663,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"食物及衛生局長陳肇始指，無任何證據顯示醫管局對早前罷工的醫護「秋後算帳」，留意到醫管局發出要求員工解釋人缺勤的信件，醫護人員對此有反應或意見，但強調醫管局有公開、透明的既定人事處理機制。她強調當局非常關心醫護人員，會盡力提供足夠資源和防疫物資。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局行政總裁高拔陞解釋，是因為醫管局月底要支付二月薪金，而目前正在集中處理疫情，未有足夠時間按程序，問清楚員工缺勤的原因，包括是否罷工，發出信件唯一目的，是發薪前告知員工日後會繼續跟進，強調會以合情合理合法方式，按法例和醫管局章程跟進。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1269797&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1269797%26csid%3D261_341&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0fUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=845be628\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1269797&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc3fd3b25dc5a9391bd0c1573024db401885f72","tid":1901663,"uid":252321,"like":34,"dislike":4,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:46:00.000Z","msg":"正苦淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e08fe3a8b810108891307afba84bd188e3bea5","tid":1901663,"uid":14918,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:46:38.000Z","msg":"語言偽術"},{"pid":"c044a1a3bc18026afa1cb28786336d271010d153","tid":1901663,"uid":11809,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:47:24.000Z","msg":"係，周梓梓陳彥霖都冇證據㗎"},{"pid":"e5806b0f43fb3ef3564533272c6b1019c8334d3e","tid":1901663,"uid":116466,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:48:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">強調會以合情合理合法方式，按法例和醫管局章程跟進</span><br />\n<br />\n即係要清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\